Web Project

Purpose

A static webpage showcasing a specific restaurant's brand, products offerings and pricing and dining experience, social media presence (Facebook, Line), contact information (phone, Line, Facebook, email) and restaurant location

• use case – 
    • b2c potential or current customers can view this page to get a general feel of the restaurant's product offering and dining experience as well as view the restaurant's business hours and holiday closings
    • b2b potential business customers can view product offerings, scale purchase options, view contact options to include: Line Messenger, FB Messenger, phone and email
    • primary viewing experience is anticipated to be via mobile with design focusing on this (mobile first)

• primary design features – 
    • header (stuck)
        X branding text/button with auto scroll to the page top
        • menu drop-down page jump select (dining/story, menu items, business hours/holidays, location (jpg map and map link), contact/social media)
        • Language Selection button (at least English and Chinese (possible Japanese and Korean))
    • main – Mobile
        • branding image
        • story text
        • menu items
        • hours
        • location
    • main – Web
        • branding image/story text (flex column/row)
        • menu items (flex column/row)
        • hours/location (flex column/row)
    footer (stuck)
        • contact (icons) – phone, email, Line, Facebook
        
Mobile Small • 320px – 413px  
Mobile Large •414px – 767 px  
Desktop/Tablet 768+px
Modal Large 310px
Modal Small 500px

Competition

• https://webdesignledger.com/restaurant-websites-to-inspire-you/

Estimated Cost

    • domain – 
        • wagui.tw ($30 initial purchase)
    • email hosting – 
        • mailbox.org (1€ per month)
    • vps hosting – ($5 per month)


Notes

• MEAN stack - mongoDB, Express, Angular, Node.js
• MEVN stack - mongoDB, Express, Vue, Node.js
• MEN stack - mongoDB, Express, (Vanilla JS) Node.js
• Apple – HIG / Google – Material Design

